OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day then remaining dry
OL,7,Fovernight with long clear spells. Some
OL,8,Fpatchy low cloud will feed in from the
OL,9,Feast. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAny early low cloud will
OL,12,Fquickly clear then a dry day with
OL,13,Fplenty of warm sunshine. Becoming very
OL,14,Fwarm in the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,17,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine
OL,18,Fand becoming very warm or hot.
